{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1771320430869}},"smart_blocks:10-试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06841577,-0.01596965,0.03877801,-0.07345382,-0.00724863,0.02447313,0.00931972,-0.02240593,0.03233778,0.00084605,0.02190305,-0.03601867,0.04661716,0.00020751,0.02724345,0.0404803,-0.02439697,-0.01905811,-0.10671979,0.00351653,0.15329185,-0.02449041,0.00256366,-0.06546628,0.04105702,0.04426083,0.01032628,-0.01575825,-0.01772573,-0.1813034,-0.00239988,0.00903913,0.01337919,0.04448202,0.04469615,-0.06720842,-0.02108237,0.05937686,-0.07811532,0.04291021,-0.00510706,0.0723879,0.06516106,-0.02416596,0.01472975,-0.0333465,-0.01440107,-0.03037885,0.02753041,-0.04035194,-0.04735105,-0.01795328,-0.02645263,0.03553531,0.02961818,-0.01542436,-0.01103225,0.07612816,0.04466029,-0.04232222,0.05118858,0.00691218,-0.21712284,0.00199145,0.05591433,-0.01334409,-0.0092162,-0.03547127,0.04351589,0.05344186,-0.04374888,0.02661612,0.03227697,0.04452471,-0.01516103,-0.02556684,0.0351174,-0.01283981,-0.0795135,-0.02027093,-0.01728882,0.08637772,0.03760896,0.00920422,-0.00014357,0.00386163,0.00942947,-0.05139923,-0.02053179,-0.04996789,-0.0040615,-0.00617413,0.00442153,0.05470385,-0.04060316,-0.00868257,0.03272601,0.02625505,-0.02714205,0.10076123,-0.0347329,0.07818688,-0.01415623,-0.10791974,0.00249718,-0.05407114,-0.04233832,-0.07330999,-0.04738191,-0.03481252,-0.03127508,-0.02324422,0.07236838,-0.07005965,-0.00991103,-0.01157017,0.06831663,0.03557876,-0.02068391,-0.02209428,0.03636778,0.05764068,0.02803254,-0.04936813,-0.01171466,-0.05993366,0.03515536,-0.00719679,0.06058815,0.07172015,0.04175207,-0.01655023,0.04323171,0.0